<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǒ yào yīn yé hé huá xǐ lè 迦南880</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ yào yīn yé hé huá huān xīn, yīn jiù wǒ de shén xǐ lè.
 zhǔ yé hé huá shì wǒ de lì liàng, shì tā zhěng jiù le wǒ.
 wǒ cái néng zhàn zài shèng diàn, kāi kǒu chàng zàn měi gē.
 yǒng yuǎn zàn měi tā, yǒng yuǎn zàn měi tā. huó shuǐ rú jiāng hé,
 huó shuǐ rú jiāng hé, huó shuǐ rú jiāng hé.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>880</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>